Concentration =  100% = 3% 100 g 	  For some problems that are more challenging, go to these URLs: URL (4:03) URL (3:39) You Try It! Problem: A 1 L container of juice drink, called brand A, contains 250 mL of juice. The rest of the drink is water. How concentrated is brand A juice drink? Problem: A 600 mL container of another juice drink, called brand B, contains 200 mL of juice. Which brand of juice drink is more concentrated, brand A or brand B? 
